<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-74-0175 </DOCNO><TEXT>A brief report is given on a joint German-Chinese project on the use ofrenewable energies in the agricultural area in the region of Daxing,China. Two different areas are tackled. The first is in the field oftechnology and includes active solar, wind energy and biogas systems.The second is concerned with the architectural aspects of the settlementand involves building design using passive solar systems. (U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>